{"tid":2289348,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"「最美小三」韓素希發狠剪短了！網驚「根本學生妹」已戀愛","createTime":"2020-11-17T08:01:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-17T13:14:32.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0da31cbadb50ff66d633dee82802251028b865f8","tid":2289348,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T08:01:41.000Z","msg":"今年衝上收視高峰的韓劇《夫婦的世界》，捧紅了「最美小三」韓素希，她從一出道就因為神似女神宋慧喬而受到矚目，現在演技也受到肯定，戲劇播畢後，她更成為新一代的「代言女王」，最近她剪去多年長髮，及肩的俏麗短髮更顯立體五官，微微亂翹的髮尾讓粉絲直呼：「太可愛了！完全學生妹！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/05/02/2533709-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F05%2F02%2F2533709-XXL.jpg&h=7a25fb10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲戲劇《夫婦的世界》爆紅的「小三」韓素希 。（圖／愛奇藝台灣站提供）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/05/02/2533092-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F05%2F02%2F2533092-XXL.jpg&h=e9efff36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲韓劇《夫婦的世界》小三韓素希成為最新「帶貨女王」。（圖／翻攝自IG）<br />\n<br />\n25歲韓素希以戲劇爆紅，一頭溫柔暖棕色長髮受到廠商青睞，成為髮品LOREAL Paris 巴黎萊雅代言人，最近她卻剪去一頭浪漫長髮，在IG發佈及肩短髮，只見她身穿白色背後深V蕾絲上衣，以超甜美的眼神回眸一笑，粉絲才發現：「原來女神真的剪短頭髮了！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/11/17/2886161-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F11%2F17%2F2886161-PH.jpg&h=e179b642&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼▲韓素希剪短髮了。（圖／翻攝自IG）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/11/17/2886160-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F11%2F17%2F2886160-PH.jpg&h=20f76982&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最近不少韓國女星通通都剪短髮亮相，像是少女時代成員潤娥，也為戲發狠剪短，潤娥的短髮與韓素希不同，潤娥的髮尾層次比較高，帶點羽毛剪的處理，顯得不厚重又輕盈，髮尾呈現自然微翹，比韓素希又多點成熟感。<br />\n<br />\n加上潤娥因為戲劇《HUSH》造型需求，不僅剪了短髮之外，在穿搭上面也更加穩重成熟，幾乎都以深色高領為主，襯托出角色該有的知性與俐落感，扎起小馬尾也十分有精神，即便粉絲大多都覺得還看不習慣，但也慢慢接受女神如此勇敢的大突破！"},{"pid":"484b33b8ff99051d6413550eb01393dd4ac196f7","tid":2289348,"uid":261849,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T08:05:40.000Z","msg":"一般貨式"},{"pid":"52f2b3b6e01133c3d9dabfdcd97cf990db9a8ceb","tid":2289348,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"484b33b8ff99051d6413550eb01393dd4ac196f7","tid":2289348,"uid":261849,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T08:05:40.000Z","msg":"一般貨式"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T08:06:35.000Z","msg":"可以算中上<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6359ec5100d804f1e609bd5325e7fd679a292b7","tid":2289348,"uid":238415,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T08:08:29.000Z","msg":"長好睇好撚多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6cd43431cefd53d43c3d6396fa2dca5f871453f","tid":2289348,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T08:10:00.000Z","msg":"越短越好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b82a650865c466f02f5e2b972392c64019190cf","tid":2289348,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e6359ec5100d804f1e609bd5325e7fd679a292b7","tid":2289348,"uid":238415,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T08:08:29.000Z","msg":"長好睇好撚多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T08:12:44.000Z","msg":"靚女一定要carry到短<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd600b276b59397a55c4566e8b02c8aa909b1cc3","tid":2289348,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f6cd43431cefd53d43c3d6396fa2dca5f871453f","tid":2289348,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T08:10:00.000Z","msg":"越短越好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fac